text: Tiago Adan Fonseca or simply Tiago Adan (born 14 March 1988 in Votorantim), is a Brazilian striker who is currently playing for the Brazilin club América de Natal. ==References== ==External links== * Player profile on Astra Ploieşti website Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian footballers Category:FC Astra Giurgiu players Category:Club Athletico Paranaense players Category:Association football forwards
